-- New Zealand Targets $307 Million of Savings From Defense Forces by 2015
-- B y   T r a c y   W i t h e r s
-- 2010-11-01T20:19:45Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-11-01/new-zealand-targets-307-million-of-savings-from-defense-forces-by-2015.html
New Zealand expects to save as much
as NZ$400 million a year within its defense forces by 2015 that
can be redirected for front-line requirements, according to a
government white paper published today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Tracy Withers at 
 twithers@bloomberg.net  